2002-1982 (La. 10/23/02)

Stanley MALCOMB and Rebecca Malcomb v. KOCH PIPELINE COMPANY, Dupree Hunting Club, and Scottsdale Insurance Co. No. 2002-CC-1982. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 23, 2002.

In re Dupree Hunting Club; Scottsdale Insurance Co.; — Defendant(s); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of St. Charles, 29th Judicial District Court Div. E, No. 56,191; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, No. 02-C-525.

Denied.

TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ.
